   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="poem" xml:id="far_off_shore">
            <head>FAR OFF-SHORE.</head>
            
            <lg type="stanza">
               <l>LOOK, the raft, a signal flying,</l>
               <l rend="indent2">Thin—a shred;</l>
               <l>None upon the lashed spars lying,</l>
               <l rend="indent2">Quick or dead.</l>
            </lg>
            
            <lg type="stanza">
               <l>Cries the sea-fowl, hovering over,</l>
               <l rend="indent2"><quote>“Crew, the crew?”</quote></l>
               <l>And the billow, reckless rover,</l>
               <l rend="indent2">Sweeps anew!</l>
            </lg>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
